           SHORT="A tool to help backing up DVDs."
cat << EOF
Vamps is a tool to help backing up DVDs: Vamps evaporates DVD compliant MPEG2
program streams by selectively copying audio and subpicture tracks and by
re-quantizing the video stream. Shrink ratio may be based on video only or on
the full PS.
EOF
